snippet.title: The Finals: Next Stage Trailer – PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Season 5 of The Finals lands on December 12, introducing a new map, two new weapons, and new gadgets including a gravity vortex and the player-tethering Lockbolt Launcher. https://store.steampowered.com/app/2073850/THE_FINALS/
